data.description: This fantastic 3-bedroom home in the Vail School district boasts a large entertainer's kitchen and a spacious layout. The kitchen offers ample cabinet and counter space, island seating, and a large pantry. High vaulted ceilings and a thoughtful layout give this home a good flow and spacious feel. The community offers a park with a basketball court and ramada for friends and family to gather. Featuring a new roof, freshly painted interior, newer AC, and water heater, this home is just waiting for you to make it your own.
